    - target: {fileID: 7928974988864360270, guid: 14e076341535d5b4ab926e4563028626, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Thank you for completing the tutorial! Now that you''ve turned in the
        Shark Idol, new spells are available. Try holding the mouse button when casting
        your water spell to summon a raincloud.

